Dentists of Miami Gardens,"17776 NW 57th Ave, Hialeah, FL 33015",(786) 579-1206,https://www.dentistsofmiamigardens.com/?sc_cid=GBP%3AO%3AGP%3A766%3AOrganic_Search%3AGeneral%3Ana&_vsrefdom=organic_gbp&y_source=1_MTU1NzEwNTAtNzE1LWxvY2F0aW9uLndlYnNpdGU%3D,4.7,333,Dentist,ChIJ-3vlOVSl2YgRrsB1xt7Z1Gw,dentists in miami,"Local Dentist Office in Hialeah FL | Dentists of Miami Gardens Supercharge your dental benefits. 20% off dentistry*, schedule today! Here to Help You Find Answers Quick Links FIRST VISIT PAY YOUR BILL MEET THE TEAM PATIENT PORTAL FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS INSURANCE ACCEPTED OUR TEAM SERVICES Overview CLEAR ALIGNERS CROWNS DENTAL SEALANTS DENTAL XRAYS DENTURES EMERGENCY SERVICES FILLINGS FLUORIDE TREATMENT TEETH CLEANING IMPLANTS INLAYS AND ONLAYS MOUTH GUARD ORAL CANCER SCREEN PERIODONTICS ROOT CANAL SCALING/ROOT PLANING SEDATION DENTISTRY TEETH BONDING TEETH EXTRACTIONS TOOTH BRIDGE VENEERS WHITENING WISDOM TEETH REMOVAL INSURANCE & PAYMENTS Overview Insurance Dental Plan Financing Pay Your Bill ABOUT US Overview Careers Contact FAQs Book an Appointment What To Expect Patient Portal SCHEDULE 786-579-1206 We are Dentists of Miami Gardens Take advantage of 20% Off Dentistry* and keep your smile in top shape. SCHEDULE NOW 786-579-1206 Meet Dr. Janelle Diaz I am committed to providing you with quality dental care. I aspire to make your dental experience one that is enjoyable and free of pain. MEET THE TEAM ADDRESS 786-579-1206 fax : 786-522-2672 17776 NW 57th Ave Hialeah, FL 33015 BOOK APPOINTMENT We are located on the corner of NW 57th Ave & NW 177th St, in the Wal-Mart plaza, next to Verizon BUSINESS HOURS Mon 8:00 AM - 7:00 PM Tue 8:00 AM - 7:00 PM Wed 8:00 AM - 7:00 PM Thu 8:00 AM - 7:00 PM Fri 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sat 8:00 AM - 3:00 PM Sun Closed We are excited to serve Hialeah and the surrounding communities. Book you appointment now! We also accept walk-ins and emergencies LANGUAGE SPOKEN English Spanish INSURANCE We take most major insurances, including: Aetna Ameritas Anthem Blue Cross Cigna Delta Dental Guardian MetLife United Health Care UCCI Family Dentistry in Hialeah, FL At Dentists of Miami Gardens, we prioritize your oral health because we understand its vital role in your overall well-being. Our personalized care and advanced solutions keep your smile healthy, whether youâre here for a routine cleaning or advanced procedures like a root canal or a dental bridge. In our friendly, modern environment, we make every visit easy and comfortable for patients of all ages. Beyond your smile, weâre dedicated to supporting your overall health at every step. Schedule your appointment today and experience a healthier smile right here in Hialeah, FL. We Pride Ourselves on Our Service When you choose Dentists of Miami Gardens, you step into a new era of dental excellence with our advanced, proven technology. Explore the advantages of transformative technology, such as Digital X-Rays and CERECÂź CAD/CAM single-visit crowns. VIEW ALL SERVICES EMERGENCY SERVICES CROWNS FILLINGS CLEAR ALIGNERS FLUORIDE TREATMENT TEETH CLEANING IMPLANTS DENTAL SEALANTS MOUTH GUARD ORAL CANCER SCREENING DENTAL X-RAYS AND IMAGING PERIODONTICS ROOT CANAL/ENDODONTICS DENTURES INLAYS AND ONLAYS SCALING AND ROOT PLANING SEDATION TEETH BONDING TOOTH BRIDGE TEETH EXTRACTIONS VENEERS WHITENING WISDOM TEETH/ORAL SURGERY Special Offers 20% Off Dentistry* Get a super start to the new year when you use your new dental benefits. SCHEDULE NOW Generations of Smiles Issue 21 Dear Heart, Your Mouth May Know Something You Don't. READ NOW OralFitnessCheck Âź Take proactive steps to better health. Ask at your next appointment for your complementary initial screening. LEARN MORE Trusted by Families Across Hialeah, FL 5.0 Came in as a new customer and let me sayâŠ it over exceeded my expectations!!! From the moment you walk in is a family feeling. Full of care, attention and smiles. They took very good care of my teeth. After take X-rays Dr. Padron came in with Briggitte and explained everything to me step by step of my condition and what I needed. After that Lara came in and together we worked out the financials. Being a single mom is kind of difficult to spend on us but sometimes itâs needed, specially if theyâre willing to work with you. Donât hesitate great place! Thank yo",200.0,,True,True,False,[]
